    <div class="well" id="spitzers-christmas-tax-surpris" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.nysun.com/article/66382?page_no=2">Spitzer&#39;s Christmas Tax Surprise - November 14, 2007 - The New York Sun</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Cunning &#8212; Amazon.com has been told it must start collecting sales tax from New York residents, because it has &#8220;salespeople&#8221; in NY.  Those salespeople? New Yorkers with Amazon affiliate links on their website.  Wonder if this will hold&#8230;</p>

